INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS / INSTALLATIONSANLEITUNG
*********************************************************

- If you want to get up and running quickly and easily -
:~/tar -xzvf clamui-0.x.x.tar.gz
:~/cd clamui
:~/clamui/> qmake clamui.pro
:~/clamui/> make

As user root / als Benutzer root:
:~/clamui/> make install

or as non-root-user root password is required
oder als normaler Benutzer, dazu wird das root Passwort benÃ¶tigt:
:~/clamui/> su -c"make install"
password:

